<Content>Loved everything about this hotel My partner  I stayed here 6th-9th October. I was absolutely gobsmacked by the decor of the room bathroom. We got the train from the Airport, 4Euros 25. Our room was on the 21st floor with amazing views over Barcelona. We arrived the day before the grand opening  although everyone was busy, nothing was any bother. The restaurant was closed  there was a limited menu, but we got to eat there on our last night. The 360 degree view was awesome  the ambience was delightful. Recommended it to my friend who is going this week 9th December. She won't be disappointed! 
